      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WINSOME JET (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at Wentworth Park in a handy 29.62 beating Magic Bandit. Comes through a solid form race last start. Ideally placed to take this out. CANYA MAYHEM (2) ran below best last time finishing fifth (30.31) over 520m at this track in a OPEN. Won at his only start from this draw. Key runner on best form. DISTINCTION (3) scored (29.38) last time out at Sandown in a Grade 4/5 and will break from box 3 for the first time. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Deserves serious consideration again. MISS ENVY (6) will be hard to beat with a drop in journey.",
